## Conclusion
ଓଡ଼ିଆ: ଏହି କାହାଣୀ ଦର୍ଶାଏ ଯେ ବୁଦ୍ଧିମାନ ଭାବରେ ଗଣିତ ପ୍ରୟୋଗ କରିବା ଦ୍ୱାରା କଷ୍ଟକର ସମସ୍ୟାଗୁଡ଼ିକର ସମାଧାନ ହୋଇପାରିବ ଏବଂ ଏହା ସମସ୍ତଙ୍କ ପାଇଁ ଲାଭଦାୟକ ହୋଇପାରେ।
This story beautifully illustrates that complex problems (ସମସ୍ୟା) can be solved with simple, clever mathematical thinking. The young math-man's wisdom not only resolved the brothers' quarrel but also highlighted the power and elegance of numbers. It teaches us that sometimes, a slight change in perspective or adding a temporary resource can lead to an optimal solution (ସମାଧାନ) for all involved.
